&lt;li&gt;Create diverse content types, including video, social media templates, and visual assets, ensuring adherence to brand style guides and relevant tone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce various video formats, including but not limited to:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Live events/event highlights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interviews/talking heads&lt;/li&gt;
