&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver social media campaigns that align with client (e.g., QF&#39;s) brand objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Collaboration &amp;amp; Market Understanding:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide clear direction and support to the team in achieving business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate a strong understanding of market dynamics and brand positioning within the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills &amp;amp; Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Proficiency:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
