&lt;h3&gt;About Ogilvy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Ogilvy was founded in 1948 by David Ogilvy. David created a culture that deeply respects and cares about its people and clients. Our mission is to inspire people and brands to make an impact and we are committed to attracting, growing, and retaining the best talent in the industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;815&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;366&quot;&gt;Memac Ogilvy is looking for an English Copywriter who will be embedded at the client’s office in Dammam.&lt;/strong&gt; In this role, the Copywriter will be responsible for taking the client’s advertising brief and generating original copy ideas that capture the attention of the target audience. They will contribute to creating campaigns that have an instant, positive impact on consumers in order to promote the product or brand being advertised. This may include developing straplines, slogans, body copy, jingles, and scripts that accompany advertising visuals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;822&quot; data-end=&quot;1024&quot;&gt;Copywriters will work in close partnership with Art Directors and contribute to the visual elements of campaigns as well. A Copywriter at Ogilvy produces big-picture advertising for big-picture clients.&lt;/p&gt;
