&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;614&quot; data-end=&quot;656&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;616&quot; data-end=&quot;656&quot;&gt;Developing creative ideas and concepts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;657&quot; data-end=&quot;701&quot;&gt;
