&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;702&quot; data-end=&quot;748&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;704&quot; data-end=&quot;748&quot;&gt;Updating digital media with timely content&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;749&quot; data-end=&quot;802&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;751&quot; data-end=&quot;802&quot;&gt;Amending and revising campaigns based on feedback&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;803&quot; data-end=&quot;846&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;805&quot; data-end=&quot;846&quot;&gt;Overseeing campaigns through production&lt;/p&gt;
