&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We work on a variety of formats: website banners, CRM emails, social content, out of home advertising and in-store executions. We are looking for a versatile thinker that can translate concepts across many platforms,&amp;nbsp;formats&amp;nbsp;and sizes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
