&lt;h3&gt;About Ogilvy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Ogilvy was founded in 1948 by David Ogilvy. David created a culture that deeply respects and cares about its people and clients. Our mission is to inspire people and brands to make an impact and we are committed to attracting, growing, and retaining the best talent in the industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MailCompose&quot;&gt;We are looking for a highly organized, detail-oriented, and creative &lt;strong&gt;Saudi National &lt;/strong&gt;Junior Account Executive Intern to support communications, reporting, and social media efforts across key client accounts. The ideal candidate is passionate about public relations, media, digital trends, and sports sponsorships with a strong ability to write, monitor, and ideate across multiple platforms. This role will also support campaign development, presentation preparation, and content planning for high-profile clients, including football team sponsorship initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Monitoring&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare daily, weekly, and monthly coverage reports for clients, consolidating media and social media mentions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct daily media monitoring, flagging priority coverage, industry updates, or reputational risks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain real-time tracking sheets and ensure accurate documentation of earned media.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft and format Minutes of Meetings (MoM) following internal and client meetings, ensuring timely distribution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Football Sponsorship Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the day-to-day coordinator for the sponsorship account.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose creative post ideas, engaging captions, and a structured content calendar tailored to campaign timelines and objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with creative, strategy, and client service teams to ensure timely approvals and content rollout.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track performance metrics, audience sentiment, and engagement to provide data driven insights and optimizations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Social Media Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively contributes to the ideation, execution, and management of social media content for various clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research trending topics, formats, and hashtags to inform content planning.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support in community management, responding to audience engagement and flagging key insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in reporting on social media KPIs and campaign performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Campaign &amp;amp; Presentation Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the development of campaign proposals, including idea generation, mood boards, and visual directions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help prepare presentations and client decks for campaign pitches, reports, and strategic planning.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to bring creative campaign ideas to life and ensure alignment with brand tone and objectives.&lt;/li

&lt;div class=&quot;page&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;layoutArea&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;column&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled Motion Graphics Designer &amp;amp; AI Video Animator to join our creative team. The ideal candidate is a versatile visual creator with strong experience in Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects, and a solid foundation in 3D software (Cinema 4D, Blender, or similar). You should be able to edit, animate, composite, and enhance video content, while also leveraging AI video-generation tools to produce cutting-edge visual assets.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edit and assemble video content using Adobe Premiere Pro, ensuring smooth pacing, storytelling, and high production value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic motion graphics, typography animations, and visual effects using Adobe After Effects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Composite layered scenes, apply transitions, color corrections, tracking, mask animations, and advanced visual treatments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and animate 3D elements using 3D software (Cinema 4D, Blender, Maya, 3ds Max etc.) when required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI video-generation tools (e.g., Mid journey, Veo, Runway...) and craft effective AI prompts to create or enhance video scenes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with creative directors, editors, and marketing teams to translate briefs into polished visual outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain consistent brand identity across all video deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize workflows, organize project files, and ensure best practices in rendering and output.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on new trends in animation, AI video generation, and creative technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience as a Motion Graphics Designer, Video Editor, or Animator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in Adobe Premiere Pro &amp;amp; After Effects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of 3D workflows; experience in Cinema 4D, Blender, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI video tools, prompt creation, and video-to-video or text-to-video pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good sense of timing, rhythm, and visual storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work under tight deadlines and handle multiple projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative problem-solving skills and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio showcasing motion graphics, animation, and AI-enhanced work is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with sound design basics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge in color grading (Lumetri, DaVinci).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in graphic design, branding, or advertising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of VFX techniques (tracking, rotoscoping, blending modes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

